Console baud rate:
  SUP, TCC: 9600
  MB/MV: 115200

Here is how the confreg in rommon should be set:
'confreg 0x8100' will set it to console speed 9600
'confreg 0x9920' will set it to console speed 115200
'confreg 0x9922' will set it to console speed 115200 and autoboot
'confreg 0x8102' will set it to console speed 9600 and autoboot

If rommon setting is corrupted, you can restore it to the default by erasing
the nvram(rommon) partition in the flash.

