Configuring multicast video sessions:

# Enable multicast routing
ip multicast-routing 

# Configure the uplink interface (L3 with PIM enabled)
int g1/3
ip address 192.168.1.1 255.255.255.0
ip pim sparse-dense-mode

# Configure SSM address range (otherwise all multicast will be considered ASM)
ip pim ssm default       ; SSM address starting from 232.0.0.1

# Configure multicast uplink
cable video multicast uplink g1/3 bandwidth 100000000

# Configure video session labels
cable video labels
ssm SSM1 source 1.1.1.1 group 232.1.1.1 bitrate 3500000

# Configure video session
int qam 3/1.1
cable video multicast SSM1 program 1

