Configuration for multicast video session with an intermediate router between
the source and the RFGW:

- Enable multicast routing on all routers and RFGW:
ip multicast-routing

- Pick one of the IP addresses on the path as RP, and configure RP address
  on all routers and RFGW:
ip pim rp-address <ip>

- Configure all the interface in between L3, and the correct pim mode
ip pim sparse-dense-mode


If Ineoquest is used as the video server:

- Make sure the source address is in the same subnet as the next hop.
- Make sure the mac address is computed based on the destination address.
  The Calc Mac Addr button will do that for you.


